The clueless scroll is obtained after completing 400 medium clue scrolls. It is considered a fun weapon.

If a player attempts to read the scroll, it will give the message: "You attempt to make out the text, but it makes no sense whatsoever."

This item can be stored in the treasure chest of a costume room. If lost, it can be re-obtained by completing another medium clue scroll.
